title: This Week - S13E17 - 2015.01.29 - 468p x264

POLITICAL: This Week
On: BBC 1 HD   
Date: Thursday 29th January 2015 
Time: 23:45 to 00:30 

Andrew Neil is joined by Michael Portillo, Alan Johnson, Miranda Green and Vicky Pryce. Plus Esther Rantzen looks at being Jewish in Britain and George Zach on the Greek election. Crack open the Blue Nun and prepare to watch public service broadcasting at its best.
